    "shortHook": "REMI Every Friday night, he sits in the corner of the bar, eyeing me over a glass of whiskey as I play piano on stage.",
    "description": "REMI Every Friday night, he sits in the corner of the bar, eyeing me over a glass of whiskey as I play piano on stage. We’ve never said a word to each other, yet I feel… something. An attraction unlike any other.\n\nThen one night he finally approaches me.\n\nHe’s nothing but a playboy who wants to add me to his list of conquests. I can’t give in to him. Getting involved with someone like Jay would only end in heartbreak, and I’ve had my heart broken too many times before.\n\nJAY With the snap of my fingers, I could have any man on his knees… but not Remi. He’s different. Instead of falling for my charms, he calls me out on them. We clash like fire and ice, but I can’t get him out of my head.\n\nToo bad I don’t do relationships.\n\nBut there’s something about the handsome musician with the most soulful eyes I’ve ever seen that makes me wonder if, maybe, love is in the cards for me after all.\n\n*His Surrender is Book 2 in the Unexpected Love series from Jaclyn Osborn. No cheating. HEA guaranteed. Please use the 'Look Inside' feature for possible trigger warnings*",
